{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-032","title":"Sentence 32","sectionId":"sentences-031","sectionTitle":"Sentence 31-40","pageStart":222,"pageEnd":227,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":33,"duplicateEntryCount":13,"pages":[{"number":222,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 32"},{"type":"text","text":"Since the consumer considers the best fruit to be that which is the"},{"type":"text","text":"most attractive, the grower must provide products that satisfy the"},{"type":"text","text":"discerning eye."},{"type":"text","text":"因为顾客认为最好的水果应该是看起来最吸引人的，所以种植"},{"type":"text","text":"者必须提供能满足顾客挑剔眼光的产品。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句主干是The grower must provide products。句首是since引导的原"},{"type":"text","text":"因状语从句，这个从句的主干是The consumer considers the best fruit to"},{"type":"text","text":"be that，其中that是代词，指代fruit，后面的which is the most attractive"},{"type":"text","text":"是定语从句，修饰前面的代词that，表明水果应该是什么样的。句子主"},{"type":"text","text":"干中的that satisfy the discerning eye是定语从句，修饰products。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"attractive /əˈtræktɪv/ a. 吸引人的，有魅力的","headword":"attractive"},{"type":"note","text":"反义 unattractive a. 不吸引人的"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 attractiveness n. 魅力，吸引力"},{"type":"entry","text":"satisfy /ˈsætɪsfaɪ/ vt. 满足，（使）满意","headword":"satisfy"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 satisfaction n. 满意"},{"type":"text","text":"satisfactory a. 满意的"},{"type":"entry","text":"discerning /dɪˈsɜːrnɪŋ/ a. 有识别力的；有眼力的","headword":"discerning"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 discern v. 觉察出；识别"}]},{"number":223,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"discernment n. 识别能力；洞察力"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"常见水果："},{"type":"entry","text":"apricot /ˈæprɪkɑːt/ n. 杏","headword":"apricot"},{"type":"entry","text":"avocado /ˌævəˈkɑːdoʊ/ n. 鳄梨，牛油果","headword":"avocado"},{"type":"entry","text":"blackberry /ˈblækberi/ n. 黑莓","headword":"blackberry"},{"type":"entry","text":"blueberry /ˈbluːbe